data.description: Fabulous escape from the world! Borders 3,323 acres BLM. Custom lodge home designed to blend with the forest. Three pellet stoves plus heat. Giant master bath! Chair lift to main level; good well & septic. Downstairs - two garages; mechanical room; canning/wine room; 31'x13' shop; 2nd shop 20'x11'; storage 20'x 7'. Just 3 miles to Galesville Reservoir boat ramp. Nice 2nd home (see comments). Giant family room plus 13'x10' office, built-ins & adjoins full bath. Generator built in.
